h 2nd Division]]\n\n|note_res_EC=[[Boldklubben 1909|B 1909]] qualified for the [[1964\u201365 European Cup#Preliminary round|1964\u201365 European Cup preliminary round]] as league leaders after the conclusion of the spring season, and qualified for the [[1965\u201366 European Cup#Preliminary round|1965\u201366 European Cup preliminary round]] as the overall 1964 season champions.\n|note_res_ECWC=[[Esbjerg fB]] qualified for the [[1964\u201365 European Cup Winners' Cup#First round|1964\u201365 European Cup Winners' Cup first round]] by winning the [[1963\u201364 Danish Cup]].\n}}\n\n== Results ==\n{{#invoke:sports results|main\n| source = <ref name=\"has-1d1964\" /><ref name=\"df3\" /><ref name=\"pedfod\" />\n| update = complete\n| a_note = \n| matches_style = FBR\n| team1 = ABK | team2 = AGF | team3 = B93 | team4 = B01 | team5 = B03 | team6 = B09 | team7 = B13 | team8 = BBK | team9 = EFB | team10 = BKF | team11 = KBK | team12 = VBK\n| name_ABK = [[Akademisk Boldklub|Akademisk BK]]\n| name_AGF = [[Aarhus Gymnastikforening|Aarhus GF]]\n| name_B93 = [[Boldklubben af 1893|B.93]]\n| name_B01 = [[Nyk\u00f8bing Falster Boldklub af 1901|B 1901]]\n| name_B03 = [[Boldklubben 1903|B 1903]]\n| name_B09 = [[Boldklubben 1909|B 1909]]\n| name_B13 = [[Boldklubben 1913|B 1913]]\n| name_BBK = [[Br\u00f8nsh\u00f8j Boldklub|Br\u00f8nsh\u00f8j BK]]\n| name_EFB = [[Esbjerg fB]]\n| name_BKF = [[Boldklubben Frem|BK Frem]]\n| name_KBK = [[Kj\u00f8benhavns Boldklub|Kj\u00f8benhavns BK]]\n| name_VBK = [[Vejle Boldklub|Vejle BK]]\n\n| match_ABK_AGF = 0\u20131 <!--12.04.1964-->\n| match_ABK_B93 = 1\u20131 <!--24.05.1964-->\n| match_ABK_B01 = 2\u20133 <!--01.11.1964-->\n| match_ABK_B03 = 1\u20134 <!--18.04.1964-->\n| match_ABK_B09 = 1\u20134 <!--26.09.1964-->\n| match_ABK_B13 = 1\u20131 <!--02.05.1964-->\n| match_ABK_BBK = 3\u20130 <!--05.04.1964-->\n| match_ABK_EFB = 0\u20133 <!--25.10.1964-->\n| match_ABK_BKF = 1\u20130 <!--20.09.1964-->\n| match_ABK_KBK = 1\u20132 <!--20.08.1964-->\n| match_