ets ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Player\n! Club\n! Matches\n! Clean<br />sheets\n! Ref\n|-\n| \u2014\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Erik Gaardh\u00f8je]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Esbjerg fB]]\n| 20<!--Verner Beck played in the last to matches, which were not clean sheets-->\n| 5\n| <ref name=\"efbh-eg\" />\n|-\n| \u2014\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Leif Nielsen|Leif Bernhard Nielsen]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Boldklubben Frem|BK Frem]]\n| 21<!--Erik L. Nielsen played the 31 May 1964 match, which was not a clean sheet-->\n| 4\n| <ref name=\"bkf-s1964\" />\n|-\n| \u2014\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Svend Aage Rask]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Boldklubben 1909|B 1909]]\n| 22\n| 4\n| <ref name=\"b09-mh\" />\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|refs=\n<ref name=\"rsssf-1d1964\">{{cite web |last1=Elbech |first1=S\u00f8ren |title=Danish League Tables 1927-1998 |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesd/denhist.html |website=www.rsssf.com |publisher=[[Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation]] (RSSSF) |accessdate=10 April 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410131825/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesd/denhist.html |archivedate=10 April 2020 |date=17 July 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"df-dt1964\">{{cite web |last1=Thomsen |first1=Jimmie |title=Danmarksturneringen 1964, Slutstillingen, 1. division 1964, 2. division 1964, 3. division 1964 |url=https://danskfodbold.com/tabel.php?seasonid=1964 |website=danskfodbold.com |accessdate=25 March 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325224949/https://danskfodbold.com/tabel.php?seasonid=1964 |archivedate=25 March 2020 |language=da}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"has-1d1964\">{{cite web |title=Danmarksturneringen 1964 : 1. division : Stilling og resultater |url=http://www.haslund.info/10_danmark/30_danmarksturneringen/1964/div1.asp |website=www.haslund.info |accessdate=10 April 2020 |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20200410194946/http://www.haslund.info/10_danmark/30_danmarksturneringen/1964/di